{
  "stem": "20581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sasow is near-- well, you could-- there was a big town out of town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], that was about 30 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sulejow was about 10 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lviv-- Lemberg-- it was about 50 kilometers from Sasow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, our-- if you had to go-- if you want to go by train, you had to go through Sulejow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from Sulejow, you could pick up to train to go to Lviv or any other places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were already in-- in the camp, in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- it was a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was located in Sasow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was located in an area, it was called before, years ago-- which I don't even remember-- in Sasow was a big-- was famous for a big factory from paper.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to make paper, pulp paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was the man who the people, the family who owned the factory was called the [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Weiser ?] family.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had a villa in the-- it was a nice place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was outside the town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a couple of big houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is where the camp were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they-- we were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We used to go every morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We used to go to the-- to cut the woods, the trees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because we had a lot of forestry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a lot of forests nearby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to go in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to-- they used to wake us up, five o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, we didn't even had SS in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no SS or Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only thing, what we had in there was one Ukrainian policeman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other one was made up of the Jewish police, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The camp [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
